Package: ebook2pdf
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.10), calibre (>= 7.0)
Description: Ebook to PDF converter with comprehensive formatting fixes
 Converts ebook files to high-quality PDFs with automatic detection of
 book publisher type, CSS injection for justified text, centered figures,
 table formatting, math formula sizing, and auto-generated Table of
 Contents with page numbers.
 Supports single-file and batch directory conversion.
